        <abstract> 
<p>CD long anxious for new American edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> to incorporate corrections since 2d ed. [of 1860]; believes such updating has kept English and continental sales high. If Appleton unable to comply, he will ask Asa Gray to find another publisher.</p>  
<p>Mentions possible arrangements for U. S. edition of new book [<hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>].</p> 
        </abstract>
